title: Fistful of Dollars
description:
This is not the Ennio Morricone version that you see all over the torrents. This is a vinyl rip of the original movie score from Warner Brothers records. i wish the LP was in better condition. I am still looking for one in better condition and if i find one, i will remaster it and post a new torrent. I did my best to remove all the clicks in the LP that i could...but you can think of the clicks as a rustic and classic and nostalgic sound.

I hope you enjoy
